00:38:23.430 --> 00:38:24.290
Thanks.

00:38:24.290 --> 00:38:26.010
SCOTT CARPENTER:
All right, and--

00:38:26.010 --> 00:38:29.100
SRDJA POPOVIC: And I'm going to
try to put two questions there.

00:38:29.100 --> 00:38:30.850
I'm going to be cheeky.

00:38:30.850 --> 00:38:33.090
First one, you mentioned
technology and horizontal

00:38:33.090 --> 00:38:35.680
sharing and so forth.

00:38:35.680 --> 00:38:39.300
Given that governments and
dictators and intelligence

00:38:39.300 --> 00:38:41.580
agencies are basically
not only catching up,

00:38:41.580 --> 00:38:44.920
but are the leaders
now in the technology,

00:38:44.920 --> 00:38:50.280
