00:39:07.560 --> 00:39:11.340
SRDJA POPOVIC: OK, so let's
start with the domestic issues.

00:39:11.340 --> 00:39:14.440
It's a normal process that
within the two or three

00:39:14.440 --> 00:39:17.480
electoral cycles, the
old guys get elected.

00:39:17.480 --> 00:39:20.140
What I'm really thrilled
about is that in my country,

00:39:20.140 --> 00:39:22.220
these people became
electable only

00:39:22.220 --> 00:39:24.320
when they embraced
the very values we

00:39:24.320 --> 00:39:25.860
were fighting for in 2000.

00:39:25.860 --> 00:39:28.170
So you look at
Otpor! as a movement,

00:39:28.170 --> 00:39:33.870
and you say, this movement was
about peace with neighbors,

00:39:33.870 --> 00:39:35.830
being a part of
the European Union,

00:39:35.830 --> 00:39:41.890
and, of course, the very idea
of democratic freedom of press,

00:39:41.890 --> 00:39:44.200
freedom of assembly,
freedom for elections.

00:39:44.200 --> 00:39:46.525
It was when the parties
who are now in power

00:39:46.525 --> 00:39:50.990
